-- India cbank asks banks to disclose sector wise loans from FY15
-- By Suvashree Dey Choudhury and Devidutta Tripathy
-- Wed Jun 18, 2014 08:35AM EDT
-- None



MUMBAI, June 18 (Reuters) - The Reserve Bank of India asked banks to disclose sector wise loans in their financial statements from 2014/15 onwards.

